WORKS ON EVERY GUITAR :)
We created presets that sound great on every guitar. Even if you want to play heavy metal on an old Fender, the sound will still be familiar.

Currently In progress:
- Recording module
- New valve amp modelings
- New realistic effect processor pedal modelings
- Lots of performance improvements

We used to name our App “Andrig” by combining the words “android” and “guitar rig”, shortage of Android Guitar Rig application.

Deplike is a mobile application that turns your Android device into an electric and bass guitar amplifier (shortly “amp”) kit. Instead of investing in expensive and hard-to-carry amp, electric guitar players can quickly access, affordably purchase, and enjoy using Deplike easily on their mobile devices anywhere with their electric guitars.

Deplike turns your Android device into an easy-to-use Guitar Multi-Effects Processor (stompbox) and electric guitar amp kit.

Carry your whole guitar rig with you in your pocket, wherever you go.

Improve your music experience with Deplike's high quality, stunning tones.

Deplike is aiming a high-performance guitar amp, multi-effects processor and stompbox kit simulation (as much as Android allows :) ).

It has never been so simple to control all your guitar effects! With Deplike's user-friendly interface, things will never get messed up. Deplike comes with seven stomp box effect pedal.

- http://www.amazon.com/Behringer-UCG102-BEHRINGER-GUITAR-LINK/dp/B000PAPO9W/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1439559241&sr=8-1&keywords=positive+grid+irig+guitar+amp+guitar+amplitube+fender

- http://www.amazon.com/AMPLITUBE-IK-MULTIMEDIA-GUITAR-IPHONE/dp/B003W47NII/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1408547194&sr=8-1&keywords=irig+guitar+amp+guitar+amplitube+positive+grid+fender

- Android 4.1 or higher
- A USB Audio Interface* or a 4-pin stereo input cable to activate the device’s microphone feature

- 1 Input / 1-2 Output channels

We used to name our App “Andrig” by combining the words “android” and “guitar rig”, shortage of Android Guitar Rig application.

Deplike is a mobile application that turns your Android device into an electric and bass guitar amplifier (shortly “amp”) kit. Instead of investing in expensive and hard-to-carry amp, electric guitar players can quickly access, affordably purchase, and enjoy using Deplike easily on their mobile devices anywhere with their electric guitars.

Deplike turns your Android device into an easy-to-use Guitar Multi-Effects Processor (stompbox) and electric guitar amp kit.

Carry your whole guitar rig with you in your pocket, wherever you go.

Improve your music experience with Deplike's high quality, stunning tones.

Deplike is aiming a high-performance guitar amp, multi-effects processor and stompbox kit simulation (as much as Android allows :) ).

It has never been so simple to control all your guitar effects! With Deplike's user-friendly interface, things will never get messed up. Deplike comes with seven stomp box effect pedal.

WORKS ON EVERY GUITAR :)
We created presets that sound great on every guitar. Even if you want to play heavy metal on an old Fender, the sound will still be familiar.

Currently In progress:
- Recording module
- New valve amp modelings
- New realistic effect processor pedal modelings
- Lots of performance improvements

We used to name our App “Andrig” by combining the words “android” and “guitar rig”, shortage of Android Guitar Rig application.

Deplike is a mobile application that turns your Android device into an electric and bass guitar amplifier (shortly “amp”) kit. Instead of investing in expensive and hard-to-carry amp, electric guitar players can quickly access, affordably purchase, and enjoy using Deplike easily on their mobile devices anywhere with their electric guitars.

Deplike turns your Android device into an easy-to-use Guitar Multi-Effects Processor (stompbox) and electric guitar amp kit.

Carry your whole guitar rig with you in your pocket, wherever you go.

Improve your music experience with Deplike's high quality, stunning tones.

Deplike is aiming a high-performance guitar amp, multi-effects processor and stompbox kit simulation (as much as Android allows :) ).

It has never been so simple to control all your guitar effects! With Deplike's user-friendly interface, things will never get messed up. Deplike comes with seven stomp box effect pedal.



Compatible Devices and Cables:

- http://www.amazon.com/Behringer-UCG102-BEHRINGER-GUITAR-LINK/dp/B000PAPO9W/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1439559241&sr=8-1&keywords=positive+grid+irig+guitar+amp+guitar+amplitube+fender

- http://www.amazon.com/Griffin-Technology-GuitarConnect-Cable-iPhone/dp/B003VWZJEQ/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&qid=1408547194&sr=8-2&keywords=irig+guitar+amp+guitar+amplitube+positive+grid+fender

- http://www.ebay.com/itm/IK-Multimedia-iRig-Guitar-Adapter-for-iphone-ipod-ipad-/331228089924?pt=Other_Tablet_eReader_Accessories&hash=item4d1ebb8e44

- http://www.amazon.com/AMPLITUBE-IK-MULTIMEDIA-GUITAR-IPHONE/dp/B003W47NII/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1408547194&sr=8-1&keywords=irig+guitar+amp+guitar+amplitube+positive+grid+fender


Requirements:
- Android 4.1 or higher
- A USB Audio Interface* or a 4-pin stereo input cable to activate the device’s microphone feature

*The USB Audio interface must meet these requirements:
- 16-bit Bit-depth
- 48kHz sampling rate
- 1 Input / 1-2 Output channels

descriptionHtml:
Deplike lets you enjoy a full studio guitar setup from your phone and tablet. Install Deplike and get your dream pedalboard, amps and cabinets in your pocket.
Easy to use, plug and play experience.
Connect your guitar to your mobile device and use guitar effects pedals, real tube amps and cabinets from your phone or tablets.

Deplike Features:

12 Electric, 2 Bass, 1 Acoustic Guitar Amps & Cabinets | 15 great sounding Amp simulations with low latency

Tangerine Rocker 100
SLO 100
Dual Recto
JCM800
P-5550
JTM45
SVT Bass
Deplike Wapi
BassBoy
Fox AC30
Deplike Acoustic Amp
Deplike Deluxe (free)
Deplike ANRG
Deplike Crafter
Deplike DST (free)

Deplike also offers 21 Guitar Effects Pedals which are: Classic Overdrive, OD 808, MetalHead Distortion, Full Blast Distortion, Dr. Muff Fuzz, 1176 Compressor, Noise Gate, Sustainer, Tremolo, Chorus, AutoWah, Flanger, Phaser, Pitch Shifter, Octaver, Delay, Tape Delay, Reverb, Roads Reverb, 5 Band Equalizer EQ, Looper pedal

Guitar Tuner, Backing track and preset sharing are additional features for guitarists to feel home!

We created presets that sound great on every guitar.


Watch the "how to connect" video: https://youtu.be/e_tqGqL0Iog

Join the community and learn more about the guitar.
https://www.facebook.com/groups/deplike/

Join the forum:
https://forum.deplike.com/

Do you have a question? Contact Us.
hello@deplike.com

YouTube Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/c/deplike

SoundCloud Page for sample sounds:
https://soundcloud.com/deplike

Web Site: https://deplike.com


Deplike (Andrig) is a mobile application that turns your Android device into an electric and bass guitar amplifier kit. Instead of investing in an expensive and hard-to-carry amp, electric guitar players can quickly access, affordable purchase, and enjoy using Deplike easily on their mobile devices anywhere with their electric guitars.

Deplike is aiming for a high-performance guitar amp, multi-effects processor and stompbox kit simulation with low latency.
